{"tid":1127392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國民黨立委黃昭順：修《兩岸條例》讓陸配能盡孝道　立意良善勿無限上綱","createTime":"2019-04-27T05:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T09:10:17.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"60516c5b3c737e84c4f11e2a273e2776a19c1b26","tid":1127392,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:43:31.000Z","msg":"黃昭順：修《兩岸條例》讓陸配盡孝道　立意良善勿無限上綱<br />\n<br />\n2019/04/26<br />\n<br />\n國民黨立委黃昭順日前提案修正《台灣地區與大陸地區人民關係條例》第16條，增列「符合《長期照顧服務法》第三條第一款、第二款、第三款者」，得申請定居，但卻遭網友批評是讓台灣門戶洞開，讓中國人入侵，淪中國人的長照天堂。黃昭順今天接受《蘋果新聞網》電話訪問喊冤說，這個提案本意良善，只是希望讓在台灣的陸配能盡孝道，完全無涉居住權、工作權、健保、長照等內容，這都是因為選舉將近，刻意無限上綱。<br />\n<br />\n黃昭順表示，由於過去中國推動一胎化政策，許多陸配的父母遠在中國無人照顧，因此基於良善與人道的立場研擬修法，但是卻遭到惡意的無限上綱，說是要佔用台灣健保資源、放寬工作權、居住權等，根本是看到黑影就開槍，真要做到運用健保資源、工作權等，都需要修正其他法案，但目前根本也都沒有提出。黃昭順嘆，現在選舉要到了，所有人道關懷就全部放下吧，該修正案也已經撤案。<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190426/1556915/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190426%2F1556915%2F&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=6342fc4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190426%2F1556915%2F&h=9906aab3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190426/1556915/</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n支那人倫理邏輯"},{"pid":"077728341f6ae7e2103dc37d39482b13e487e8bb","tid":1127392,"uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"陸配要盡孝道<br />\n照顧以前子女<br />\n咪返中國居住<br />\n<br />\n香港殖民環團聚咪返去大灣區"},{"pid":"98ac5167b5cd45d104ee89989c40090d775b1646","tid":1127392,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T06:04:36.000Z","msg":"變成昨日香港，今日台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7626796b660ea8440af9a0a544ce5e28472fc9fd","tid":1127392,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T08:05:34.000Z","msg":"要唔要訂個150人/日嘅單程證名額?"},{"pid":"5ac054cddd5b6abe87ba5e111fda4c03d37ce9c4","tid":1127392,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T08:08:38.000Z","msg":"國民黨&gt;讓陸配能盡孝道&gt;天天天藍&gt;恩公&gt;共產黨"},{"pid":"a32cafc4847f2e4ceb21d89f57a9d2d99ca8fc3a","tid":1127392,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T08:50:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">中國</span>國民黨&gt;讓<del>陸</del><span style=\"color: red;\">中國</span>配能盡孝道&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">中國國國民黨俱樂部MyRadio既</span>天天天藍&gt;恩公&gt;<span style=\"color: red;\">中國</span>共產黨</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2fc578ba3b0dc1950b3323aa9fa989cc8c08afcb","tid":1127392,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:08:03.000Z","msg":"返大陸團聚！"},{"pid":"eec26b8ec378291c94435b246a2b0a567b71b570","tid":1127392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fc578ba3b0dc1950b3323aa9fa989cc8c08afcb","tid":1127392,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:08:03.000Z","msg":"返大陸團聚！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:09:23.000Z","msg":"大灣區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7e24818e4e9439b5183d17fd4b0dcbb4fcb9f0","tid":1127392,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"支那人又用民主同道德綁架人<br />\n早提唔提依家先提個議案<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}